  <h1>A7  Cross-site Scripting (XSS)</h1>
  <p class="muted">Injection of untrusted content into web pages that is interpreted by the browser.</p>
  <h3>Mitigations</h3>
  <ul><li>Escape output by default (Jinja does this unless |safe is used).</li><li>Sanitize or whitelist allowed markup using a library (e.g., Bleach) if HTML is required.</li><li>Use CSP headers to limit allowed script sources.</li></ul>
  <h3>Where to patch</h3>
  <p>Remove uses of <code>|safe</code> and sanitize review/comment inputs.</p>
